She was pleased to have recieved an asignment.
"Yes Mgatron.  As you requested.  It shall be done."

She turned and walked down the hallway to where Quickstrike and Black 
Arachnis were talking.

"Sorry to interupt.  But Megatron has ordered that Quickstrike and I do some 
recon work at Hellbeast's construstion protject.  We can leave as soon as 
your ready Commander Quickstrike."
She turned and walked out of the room.  She leaned against the wall near the 
doorway, but out of ear shot.  She didn't like easedropping unless it was 
nessessary.  And easedropping on one's commander wasn't nessessary.
